name: Linq2vso
tagline: Linq provider for Visual Studio Online API
body:
### Linq2VSO
Linq2VSO is a Linq provider to access to yout Visual Studio Online account, projects, tasks, etc...

### Current Status
In development. Currenlty non-functional

### Authors and Contributors
Created and mantained by @cjgaliana, based on [Linq2Twiiter](https://github.com/JoeMayo/LinqToTwitter) created by Joe Mayo (@JoeMayo)
